[src:profiling-continuous/sampling-signal-processing] The sampling rates and resolutions in both spatial directions can be measured in units of lines per picture height.
[src:profiling-continuous/sampling-signal-processing] Spatial aliasing of high-frequency luma or chroma video components shows up as a moiré pattern.
